    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable wear including minor dents and scratches with some paint fading, but no major structural damage. The interior has visible wear on the upholstery and trim, though it remains functional. The mechanical systems are operational but may require some attention in the near term. A reasonable option for a buyer looking for basic transportation at a modest price.",
