    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is offered in true mint condition and represents a rare opportunity to own a car that looks, feels, and performs as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The engine runs flawlessly, delivering smooth, responsive power with no hesitation, unusual noises, or mechanical concerns of any kind. The exterior paint retains its full original luster with no scratches, dents, or blemishes, and all body panels are perfectly aligned. The interior is immaculate \u2014 seats, carpeting, headliner, and all trim pieces show zero wear, and every electronic feature, control, and comfort system functions exactly as intended. This is a turnkey vehicle requiring absolutely no immediate investment; a pre-purchase inspection is warmly welcomed and will confirm everything described here.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 An Honest Fair-Condition Find! This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to serve as your reliable daily driver. You'll notice some visible wear on the exterior and interior that comes with a well-used vehicle, but the mechanicals are functional and it's ready to hit the road. A great opportunity for a practical buyer looking for honest transportation at a fair price \u2014 what you see is what you get, and that's something you can count on!",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
